OL,4,CSri Lanka to ban burka and other face
OL,5,Ccoverings
OL,6, Sri Lanka has taken a significant step
OL,7, towards banning the burka and other
OL,8, face coverings in public, on grounds of
OL,9, national security.
OL,11,FPublic Security Minister Sarath
OL,12,FWeerasekara told the BBC that he had
OL,13,Fsigned a cabinet order which now needs
OL,14,Fparliamentary approval.
OL,16,FOfficials say they expect the ban to be
OL,17,Fimplemented very soon.
OL,19,FThe move comes nearly two years after a
OL,20,Fwave of co-ordinated attacks on hotels
OL,21,Fand churches on Easter Sunday.
